        <head>A Secret Day</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I woke up today, </l>
          <l>It was a brand new day </l>
          <l>It was a secret day </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>It was a secret day </l>
          <l>That I woke up into </l>
          <l>But no one knew about that day </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Everyone’s sleepin, </l>
          <l>And not knowing </l>
          <l>Such a brightly day for fun </l>
          <l>I went into houses playin’ around </l>
          <l>No one will ever know </l>
          <l>No one will ever know </l>
          <l>She will never know.</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
